hm the fifth king jigme khesar namgyal wangchuck may 2 (every year) - birth anniversary of third king jigme dorji wangchuck may 1 (not fixed) - shabdrung kuchoe (commemorates the passing of shabdrung ngawang namgyal in 1651 ce) june 4 (not fixed) - commemoration of lord buddha's parnirvana. june 29 (not fixed) - anniversary of the birth of guru rinpoche july 23 (not fixed) - the first sermon of lord buddha september 21 (not fixed) - thimphu drubchen (thimphu only) september 25-27 (not fixed) - thimphu tshechu(thimphu only) september 22 (not fixed) - blessed rainy day october 24 (not fixed) 